{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c8f2a1b0-4e6d-4a9c-9f1e-chat-history-only",
    "name": "Hermes Chat History API",
    "description": "MySQL 聊天记录查询接口（独立 Collection）。\n\n接口:\n- GET /api/chat/users/{user_id}/sessions\n- GET /api/chat/sessions/{session_id}/turns\n\n前置条件:\n- gateway 已启用 api_server\n- mysql_chat / HERMES_MYSQL_* 已配置\n- 对话接口需传 X-Hermes-User-Id 才会落库\n\n认证:\n- Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}（若服务端配置了 API_SERVER_KEY）",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8642"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiKey",
      "value": "replace-with-api-server-key"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "10001"
    },
    {
      "key": "sessionId",
      "value": "demo-session-id"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "GET /api/chat/users/{user_id}/sessions",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{apiKey}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/chat/users/{{userId}}/sessions?limit=20&page=1",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "chat", "users", "{{userId}}", "sessions"],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "limit",
              "value": "20",
              "description": "每页条数，默认 20，最大 100"
            },
            {
              "key": "page",
              "value": "1",
              "description": "页码，从 1 开始，默认 1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "按业务用户 ID 查询会话列表，按 updated_at 倒序（最近活跃在前）。\n\nPath:\n- user_id: 业务用户 ID\n\nQuery:\n- limit: 可选，1-100，默认 20\n- page: 可选，从 1 开始，默认 1\n\nResponse 200:\n- object, user_id, total, limit, page, sessions[]"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
          "body": "{\n  \"object\": \"list\",\n  \"user_id\": \"10001\",\n  \"total\": 1,\n  \"limit\": 20,\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"session_uid\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567\",\n      \"hermes_session_id\": \"sess_abc123\",\n      \"user_id\": \"10001\",\n      \"channel\": \"api_server\",\n      \"status\": 1,\n      \"turn_count\": 3,\n      \"last_question\": \"最近一条用户问题\",\n      \"started_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:00:00\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:30:00\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "503 MySQL unavailable",
          "status": "Service Unavailable",
          "code": 503,
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"MySQL chat persistence is not enabled\",\n    \"type\": \"service_unavailable\"\n  }\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "GET /api/chat/sessions/{session_id}/turns",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{apiKey}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/chat/sessions/{{sessionId}}/turns",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "chat", "sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "turns"]
        },
        "description": "按会话 ID 查询问答轮次，按 turn_no 升序（第 1 轮在上）。\n\nPath session_id 支持:\n- 数据库自增 id（如 1）\n- session_uid\n- hermes_session_id（X-Hermes-Session-Id）\n\nResponse 200:\n- object, session, total, turns[]\n\nResponse 404: 会话不存在"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
          "body": "{\n  \"object\": \"list\",\n  \"session\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"session_uid\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567\",\n    \"hermes_session_id\": \"sess_abc123\",\n    \"user_id\": \"10001\",\n    \"channel\": \"api_server\"\n  },\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"turns\": [\n    {\n      \"turn_no\": 1,\n      \"question_text\": \"你好\",\n      \"answer_text\": \"你好，我是 Hermes\",\n      \"status\": \"answered\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:00:01\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"turn_no\": 2,\n      \"question_text\": \"第二条问题\",\n      \"answer_text\": \"第二条回答\",\n      \"status\": \"answered\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:05:01\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "body": "{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Session not found: demo-session-id\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\"\n  }\n}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
